    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- PRP TECHNOLOGY -->\n<section class=\"prp-problem-section\">\n  <div class=\"prp-problem-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">TECHNOLOGY</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What is PRP Therapy?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) is a regenerative method that uses plasma from your own blood. It contains growth factors that help regenerate hair and support its growth and density.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"problem-grid\">\n      <div class=\"problem-card\">\n        <div class=\"problem-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M3 22V18\"/>\n            <path d=\"M7 22V14\"/>\n            <path d=\"M11 22V10\"/>\n            <path d=\"M15 22V16\"/>\n            <path d=\"M19 22V12\"/>\n            <path d=\"M21 22H3\"/>\n            <path d=\"M3 10L8 5L13 9L21 2\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Hair growth support</h3>\n        <p>Growth factors contained in the plasma stimulate hair follicles, improve blood circulation in the scalp, and help strengthen weakened hair roots.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"problem-card\">\n        <div class=\"problem-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"6\"/>\n            <path d=\"M7 6C8 4 10 3 12 3C14 3 16 4 17 6\"/>\n            <path d=\"M8 19L6 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M10 18L9 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M14 18L15 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M16 19L18 22\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Natural regeneration</h3>\n        <p>PRP therapy uses your own biological material, making it gentle and well-tolerated. It helps support scalp healing after hair transplantation.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"problem-card\">\n        <div class=\"problem-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/>\n            <path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Part of the transplant</h3>\n        <p>We apply PRP as a supportive therapy during hair transplantation. It helps accelerate scalp healing and support the growth of new hair.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .prp-problem-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n    background: var(--white);\n  }\n\n  .prp-problem-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .section-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .prp-problem-section .section-header .mh-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 8px 24px;\n    background: var(--primary-gold) !important;\n    color: var(--black) !important;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    border-radius: 30px;\n  }\n\n  .section-title {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 20px 0;\n    letter-spacing: normal;\n  }\n\n  .section-description {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .problem-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n  }\n\n  .problem-card {\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 40px 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .problem-card:hover {\n    background: var(--white);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-8px);\n  }\n\n  .problem-icon {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    margin: 0 auto 24px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n  }\n\n  .problem-icon svg {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .problem-card h3 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .problem-card p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .norwood-placeholder {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    background: rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.1);\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    border: 2px dashed var(--medium-gray);\n  }\n\n  .norwood-placeholder p {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    margin: 4px 0;\n  }\n\n  .norwood-placeholder strong {\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 1200px) {\n    .problem-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .prp-problem-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .problem-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 24px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
