    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- WHO IS IT SUITABLE FOR -->\n<section class=\"prp-vhodna-section\">\n  <div class=\"prp-vhodna-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">APPLICATION</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Who is PRP Therapy suitable for?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">PRP therapy is suitable for a wide range of clients with various needs.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"kandidati-grid\">\n      <div class=\"kandidat-item\">\n        <div class=\"kandidat-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M18 2L22 6\"/>\n            <path d=\"M7.5 20.5L3.5 16.5L15 5L19 9L7.5 20.5Z\"/>\n            <path d=\"M15 5L19 9\"/>\n            <path d=\"M11 9L15 13\"/>\n            <path d=\"M7.5 20.5L2 22L3.5 16.5\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>After transplantation</h3>\n        <p>One PRP therapy session is included in the transplant price and supports healing and growth of transplanted hair.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"kandidat-item\">\n        <div class=\"kandidat-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"6\"/>\n            <path d=\"M7 6C8 4 10 3 12 3C14 3 16 4 17 6\"/>\n            <path d=\"M8 19L6 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M10 18L9 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M14 18L15 22\"/>\n            <path d=\"M16 19L18 22\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Thinning hair</h3>\n        <p>PRP stimulates weakened hair follicles and supports hair growth during gradual thinning.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"kandidat-item\">\n        <div class=\"kandidat-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/>\n            <path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Hair loss prevention</h3>\n        <p>PRP can also be used preventively to maintain hair health and prevent hair loss.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .prp-vhodna-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n    background: var(--white);\n  }\n\n  .prp-vhodna-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .kandidati-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n    margin-top: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-item {\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 40px 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-item:hover {\n    background: var(--white);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-8px);\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-icon {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    margin: 0 auto 20px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-icon svg {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-item h3 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .kandidat-item p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 1200px) {\n    .kandidati-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .prp-vhodna-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .kandidati-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 24px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
