    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- PRP BENEFITS -->\n<section class=\"prp-metody-section\">\n  <div class=\"prp-metody-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">BENEFITS</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Why choose PRP Therapy?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">PRP therapy offers a number of benefits as a natural method of supporting hair growth.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"metody-grid\">\n      <div class=\"metoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"metoda-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"/>\n            <path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>100% natural</h3>\n        <p>PRP uses plasma from your own blood, so it contains no foreign substances. This makes the method gentle and well-tolerated.</p>\n        <ul class=\"metoda-list\">\n          <li>no chemicals</li>\n          <li>no side effects</li>\n          <li>biologically compatible</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"metoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"metoda-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M13 2L3 14H12L11 22L21 10H12L13 2Z\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Health benefits</h3>\n        <p>PRP accelerates healing, supports hair growth, and improves the overall transplant result.</p>\n        <ul class=\"metoda-list\">\n          <li>stimulation of hair follicles</li>\n          <li>support of hair tissue healing</li>\n          <li>improved scalp blood circulation</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"metoda-card\">\n        <div class=\"metoda-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/>\n            <path d=\"M12 6V12L16 14\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3>Quick application</h3>\n        <p>PRP is applied directly during hair transplantation. The process itself takes only a few minutes and minimally extends the overall procedure time.</p>\n        <ul class=\"metoda-list\">\n          <li>minimal discomfort</li>\n          <li>no extended recovery</li>\n          <li>part of the procedure</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .prp-metody-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n  }\n\n  .prp-metody-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .metody-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 40px;\n    margin-top: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-card {\n    background: var(--white);\n    border-radius: 24px;\n    padding: 48px 40px;\n    border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-card:hover {\n    border-color: var(--primary-gold);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-8px);\n  }\n\n  .metoda-icon {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n  }\n\n  .metoda-icon svg {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-card h3 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 28px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-card p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-list {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-list li {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    padding: 8px 0 8px 28px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .metoda-list li::before {\n    content: '✓';\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 0;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 992px) {\n    .metody-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .prp-metody-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .metody-grid {\n      gap: 24px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
